.TH ABRAFLEXI-UPDATEJASPERCLASSPATH 1 "2025-09-20" "abraflexi-report-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-updatejasperclasspath \- update Jasper Studio classpaths for the installed AbraFlexi version
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-updatejasperclasspath
[\fIversion\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-updatejasperclasspath
searches the current user's home directory for Eclipse
.I .classpath
files that reference AbraFlexi or FlexiBee libraries and rewrites embedded
version numbers to match the locally installed AbraFlexi version.
.PP
The tool first checks
.I /usr/share/flexibee/lib/VERSION.txt
and then
.I /usr/share/abraflexi/lib/VERSION.txt
to detect the installed version automatically.
If neither file is present, a version can be supplied explicitly as the first
argument.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I version
Optional explicit AbraFlexi version to use when no installed version can be
detected.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Use the installed AbraFlexi version:
.B abraflexi-updatejasperclasspath
.TP
Force a specific version:
.B abraflexi-updatejasperclasspath 2025.9.20
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-repxmlunpacker (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Vítězslav Dvořák
